    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Toys representing Noah's ark and associated pairs of animals; probably originated in Germany in the late 16th or early 17th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
